     </div>\n     </div>\n   </div>\n   <div id="content">\n   	<div id="main" class="left_main">\n     	<span id="hs_cos_wrapper_main" class="hs_cos_wrapper hs_cos_wrapper_widget hs_cos_wrapper_type_rich_text" style="" data-hs-cos-general-type="widget" data-hs-cos-type="rich_text"><p><span style="font-size: 16px; color: #444444;"></span><span style="color: #7d3f98; font-size: 24px;"><strong>Aetna / Coventry Medicare Advantage and PDP&nbsp;</strong><strong>Certification Details for 2019</strong></span></p>\n <p><span style="color: #3574e3;"><a href="https://aetna.cmpsystem.com/ext/ahip/login.php" rel=" noopener" target="_blank" style="color: #3574e3;"><span style="text-decoration: underline;"><span style="font-size: 16px;"><strong>https://aetna.cmpsystem.com/ext/ahip/login.php</strong></span></span></a></span></p>\n <ul>\n <li><span style="font-size: 16px; color: #444444;">2019 Aetna certification process&nbsp;<strong>starts 7/11</strong></span></li>\n <li><span style="font-size: 16px; color: #444444;">Want to save $50? Certify with us</span></li>\n <li><span style="font-size: 16px; color: #444444;">Coming soon to the Ascend app</span></li>\n <li><span style="font-size: 16px; color: #444444;">Get a discounted rate on E&amp;O insurance</span></li>\n <li><span style="font-size: 16px; color: #444444;">Make sure you do this before sales events</span></li>\n </ul>\n <p><span style="color: #7d3f98; font-size: 16px;"><strong>2019 Aetna Individual Medicare producer certification begins July 11</strong></span></p>\n <p><span style="color: #444444; font-size: 16px;">Starting July 11, you can complete the 2019 annual certification process for Aetna and Coventry Individual Medicare products (MA/MAPD, PDP). It''s one of the annual requirements you must complete to sell our 2019 plans this Annual Election Period. Watch for more details about certification later this month.</span></p>\n <p><span style="color: #7d3f98; font-size: 16px;"><strong>AHIP launches 2019 AHIP training on June 18... So why wait until July 11?</strong></span></p>\n <p><span style="color: #444444; font-size: 16px;">Simply put, because you can save money. When you complete 2019 Aetna Individual Medicare producer certification, it includes AHIP and costs $125 – That’s a savings of $50 off the retail price! Mark your calendars and plan to certify with us starting July 11.</span></p>\n <p><span style="color: #7d3f98; font-size: 16px;"><strong>Coming soon: Enhancements to the Ascend Virtual Sales Office app</strong></span></p>\n <p><span style="color: #444444; font-size: 16px;">We’ve wrapping up some cool new enhancements to our online enrollment app, the Ascend Virtual Sales Office app. Later this month, the home screen will feature a new look that makes it easier and faster for you to get where you need to go, and reach the most frequently used tools. Once the enhancements are live, after logging in, with one click you’ll be able to:</span></p>\n <ol>\n <li><span style="color: #444444; font-size: 16px;">Send a Scope of Appointment</span></li>\n <li><span style="color: #444444; font-size: 16px;">Give a sales presentation</span></li>\n <li><span style="color: #444444; font-size: 16px;">Start enrolling a client</span></li>\n <li><span style="color: #444444; font-size: 16px;">Email a quote/send an e-kit</span></li>\n <li><span style="color: #444444; font-size: 16px;">Compare plans, estimate Rx costs and lookup doctors</span></li>\n </ol>\n <p><span style="color: #444444; font-size: 16px;">Watch for more details coming soon! Not yet using the Ascend app? Once you’re “ready to sell,”&nbsp;<a href="https://urldefense.proofpoint.com/v2/url?u=http-3A__links.comms.aetna.com_ctt-3Fkn-3D19-26ms-3DMzQ3MTcxMDUS1-26r-3DMTA1ODU1MjMzMDE5S0-26b-3D0-26j-3DMTMwMTQxMzMwMQS2-26mt-3D1-26rt-3D0&amp;d=DwMFaQ&amp;c=9kXwhKegtYeqgWqETKbfKA&amp;r=LrFB0Qt62LXYkpMYf2ILCrDE2AuQDOrAtf_yBFHLvI4&amp;m=4FT3kVDlznPBuMZjcRyShz0zIFxEUhznvc32XotbAJo&amp;s=unwYga0Yz0LdLjuTYC-YNf1F4WUMMmbY2jiUpyF9SSc&amp;e=" rel=" noopener" target="_blank" style="color: #444444;">just request access on Producer World here</a>.</span></p>\n <p><span style="color: #7d3f98; font-size: 16px;"><strong>Your prospects are online – Why not enroll them online too?</strong></span></p>\n <p><span style="color: #444444; font-size: 16px;">When you enroll your clients using the Ascend Virtual Sales Office app, our electronic enrollment tool, you can:</span></p>\n <ul>\n <li><span style="color: #444444; font-size: 16px;">Shorten the sales cycle and hold more appointments</span></li>\n <li><span style="color: #444444; font-size: 16px;">Submit enrollments electronically</span></li>\n <li><span style="color: #444444; font-size: 16px;">Eliminate paperwork</span></li>\n <li><span style="color: #444444; font-size: 16px;">Reduce application errors</span></li>\n <li><span style="color: #444444; font-size: 16px;">Quickly access resources all in one place</span></li>\n </ul>\n <p><span style="color: #444444; font-size: 16px;">To start using the Ascend app, login to Producer World,&nbsp;<a href="https://urldefense.proofpoint.com/v2/url?u=http-3A__links.comms.aetna.com_ctt-3Fkn-3D14-26ms-3DMzQ3MTcxMDUS1-26r-3DMTA1ODU1MjMzMDE5S0-26b-3D0-26j-3DMTMwMTQxMzMwMQS2-26mt-3D1-26rt-3D0&amp;d=DwMFaQ&amp;c=9kXwhKegtYeqgWqETKbfKA&amp;r=LrFB0Qt62LXYkpMYf2ILCrDE2AuQDOrAtf_yBFHLvI4&amp;m=4FT3kVDlznPBuMZjcRyShz0zIFxEUhznvc32XotbAJo&amp;s=kBY218uSCGVdI4a_ET_W1VbFMn6_wWYgdyMLJzKcMrY&amp;e=" rel=" noopener" target="_blank" style="color: #444444;">go to the Ascend Virtual Sales Office</a>&nbsp;app section and then click on "request access" to get started. If you have questions about the Ascend app, just contact your local Aetna Medicare Broker Manager.</span></p>\n <p><span style="color: #7d3f98; font-size: 16px;"><strong>Compliance Connection: Complete an event verification form before sales events</strong></span></p>\n <p><span style="color: #444444; font-size: 16px;">Don’t forget to fill out an event verification form when you hold a sales meeting or event about our Individual Medicare plans. The form helps protect you and Aetna if CMS decides to audit your event. It’s easy to complete.&nbsp;<a href="https://urldefense.proofpoint.com/v2/url?u=http-3A__links.comms.aetna.com_ctt-3Fkn-3D4-26ms-3DMzQ3MTcxMDUS1-26r-3DMTA1ODU1MjMzMDE5S0-26b-3D0-26j-3DMTMwMTQxMzMwMQS2-26mt-3D1-26rt-3D0&amp;d=DwMFaQ&amp;c=9kXwhKegtYeqgWqETKbfKA&amp;r=LrFB0Qt62LXYkpMYf2ILCrDE2AuQDOrAtf_yBFHLvI4&amp;m=4FT3kVDlznPBuMZjcRyShz0zIFxEUhznvc32XotbAJo&amp;s=JxeLxKphkeL611cvEL5C4fHzNQ1MTM7HltU6F0Toqvw&amp;e=" rel=" noopener" target="_blank" style="color: #444444;">Just download the form</a>&nbsp;and print it out before your next event. Then, have the form signed by your event venue contact before your event starts. Lastly, keep the form on file. You can learn more on&nbsp;<a href="https://urldefense.proofpoint.com/v2/url?u=http-3A__links.comms.aetna.com_ctt-3Fkn-3D8-26ms-3DMzQ3MTcxMDUS1-26r-3DMTA1ODU1MjMzMDE5S0-26b-3D0-26j-3DMTMwMTQxMzMwMQS2-26mt-3D1-26rt-3D0&amp;d=DwMFaQ&amp;c=9kXwhKegtYeqgWqETKbfKA&amp;r=LrFB0Qt62LXYkpMYf2ILCrDE2AuQDOrAtf_yBFHLvI4&amp;m=4FT3kVDlznPBuMZjcRyShz0zIFxEUhznvc32XotbAJo&amp;s=F0P4QFhZ4Ldcy0mxSaAihZEP_52cu5T3BmzCQf6GSvc&amp;e=" rel=" noopener" target="_blank" style="color: #444444;">Producer World.</a></span></p>\n <p><span style="color: #444444; font-size: 16px;">Questions? We''re here to help!</span></p>\n <p><span style="color: #444444; font-size: 16px;">If you have any questions, just contact the Aetna Medicare Broker Services Department at 1-866-714-9301 or brokersupport@aetna.com.&nbsp;</span></p></span>\n     </div>\n     <div id="right">\n     </div>\n   </div>\n   <div id="footer_container">\n       <div id="footer">Copyright © 2019 Precision Senior Marketing</div>\n   </div>\n </div>\n'),
