m/final/img/common/icons/social/email-24x24.png" class="hs-image-widget hs-image-social-sharing-24" style="max-height:24px;max-width:24px;border-width:0px;border:0px;" width="24" hspace="0" alt="Share on Email"></a></span>\r\n        	</div>\r\n        \r\n      </div>\r\n    </div>\r\n  </div>\r\n  <div id="content">\r\n  	<div id="main" class="left_main">\r\n    	<span id="hs_cos_wrapper_main" class="hs_cos_wrapper hs_cos_wrapper_widget hs_cos_wrapper_type_rich_text" style="" data-hs-cos-general-type="widget" data-hs-cos-type="rich_text"><p><span style="color: #ff9900; font-size: 24px;" mce-data-marked="1"><strong>2019 Cigna-HealthSpring Certification is here!</strong></span></p>\r\n<p><span style="color: #444444; font-size: 16px;">2019 Cigna-HealthSpring Certification is here!</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="color: #444444; font-size: 16px;">Complete certification and attestation details is outlined below.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="color: #444444; font-size: 16px;">Visit <span style="text-decoration: underline; color: #3574e3;"><a href="www.cignahealthspringproducers.com" rel=" noopener" target="_blank" style="color: #3574e3;"><strong>www.cignahealthspringproducers.com</strong></a></span> to get started!</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="color: #444444; font-size: 16px;">For more information on the certification process, please <span style="text-decoration: underline; color: #3574e3;"><a href="https://urldefense.proofpoint.com/v2/url?u=http-3A__r20.rs6.net_tn.jsp-3Ff-3D0013bKLzYwtF4I6IXKwREYjn2O41pOGGIBUAiNClj28MrF-5FsXe6bdasNU7Dc8hysZWdQJTOlubqg4tWxanaM2EgvIydwCOpAhbsWuYHXtOCM4k7EStLgbg2HGWuWJoA3Su9Ztb2R1OaTbUIeBi1OKgvuH-2DFpYnmZYg-5FEx8IANyAG-2DArBInzdunFzLqrE34McS1nqeoo02DvqDzX2Cwzp5DOlxedZT-2DgqRD5oh4LSPgLKsw-3D-26c-3D3qsGT-5F65JWjWjZv49Hn8LGx-5FeQpPZFj4gm30-2DDUnBRkN8Y7AUyC6lg-3D-3D-26ch-3DQ1UanDj48hZGxI-5FKOqlau0UhMsGrUu-5FUHFpTZd66vY-5FjGndLZ91CqQ-3D-3D&amp;d=DwMFaQ&amp;c=9kXwhKegtYeqgWqETKbfKA&amp;r=piGSTfZN5S4ZQGfbjJZ3X-GFO97IFQtUcn3FNBxbF6Y&amp;m=jM_Xl7TDeEHDYRbZA_vaOqq7t5RED6AYIw9ROKDLICE&amp;s=po-_9cwtzs1U0qbku_HiCvaj7z7XUb4V1hQVUUXC2DU&amp;e=" rel=" noopener" target="_blank" style="color: #3574e3;">click here to view the 2019 Certification Roadmap</a></span>.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="color: #444444; font-size: 16px;">New and returning agents must complete certification training online.</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="color: #444444; font-size: 16px;">Local face-to-face (instructor-led) training is recommended (but not required) for 2019 selling; sign-up will be available through the online calendar later this summer.&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 20px;"><strong><span style="color: #444444;">2019 Contract and Attestation Requirements</span></strong></span></p>\r\n<p><span style="color: #444444; font-size: 16px;">Cigna-HealthSpring’s online attestation process allows Agents and Agencies to complete all required contractual updates and attestations as part of our annual agent certification process.</span></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><span style="color: #444444; font-size: 16px;">AGENTS - Agents cannot begin 2019 certification training until all contractual agreements are complete. <strong>All Agents must complete attestation requirements and certification by December 31, 2018, or forfeit renewal payments</strong>.<br><br></span></li>\r\n<li><span style="color: #444444; font-size: 16px;">AGENCIES - <strong>Agencies must complete attestation requirements by December 31, 2018, otherwise January 2019 payments will be withheld. Agencies that fail to complete these requirements by March 31, 2019, will forfeit payments</strong>. If the agency representative is also licensed and appointed with Cigna-HealthSpring, he/she will also need to log in with personal credentials to attest as an agent.<br><br></span></li>\r\n<li><span style="color: #444444; font-size: 16px;">NEW FOR 2019 - <strong>Agencies will now log in with their agency NPN numbers as usernames</strong>. Each agency will receive two separate emails; one containing the username, the other containing the current password.</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 20px;"><strong><span style="color: #444444;">2019 Certification Reimbursement</span></strong></span></p>\r\n<p><span style="color: #444444; font-size: 16px;">Cigna-HealthSpring will reimburse certification costs for 2019 Medicare Advantage agent certification, where eligibility requirements are met.</span></p>\r\n<p><strong><span style="color: #444444; font-size: 16px;">To be eligible for reimbursement you need to complete your 2019 certification by September 15, 2018 AND sell five (5) net January 1, 2019 effective applications.</span></strong></p>\r\n<p><span style="color: #444444; font-size: 16px;">After meeting these requirements, you’ll be eligible for reimbursement as outlined below:</span></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><span style="color: #444444; font-size: 16px;">Complete AHIP Training and all Cigna-HealthSpring required courses to receive $125 reimbursement</span></li>\r\n<li><span style="color: #444444; font-size: 16px;">Complete Gorman Health Group Training and all Cigna-HealthSpring required courses to receive $99 reimbursement</span></li>\r\n<li><span style="color: #444444; font-size: 16px;">Complete Pinpoint Medicare Training and all Cigna-HealthSpring required courses to receive $89.95 reimbursement</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><span style="color: #444444; font-size: 16px;">We value our partnership and look forward to a successful AEP!</span></p></span>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div id="right">\r\n    </div>\r\n  </div>\r\n  <div id="footer_container">\r\n      <div id="footer">Copyright © 2019 Precision Senior Marketing</div>\r\n  </div>\r\n</div>\r\n'),
