w.psmbrokerage.com/hs-fs/hubfs/image.jpg?width=165&amp;height=40&amp;name=image.jpg 165w, //www.psmbrokerage.com/hs-fs/hubfs/image.jpg?width=330&amp;height=79&amp;name=image.jpg 330w, //www.psmbrokerage.com/hs-fs/hubfs/image.jpg?width=495&amp;height=119&amp;name=image.jpg 495w, //www.psmbrokerage.com/hs-fs/hubfs/image.jpg?width=660&amp;height=158&amp;name=image.jpg 660w, //www.psmbrokerage.com/hs-fs/hubfs/image.jpg?width=825&amp;height=198&amp;name=image.jpg 825w, //www.psmbrokerage.com/hs-fs/hubfs/image.jpg?width=990&amp;height=237&amp;name=image.jpg 990w" sizes="(max-width: 330px) 100vw, 330px"></span>\r\n        </div>\r\n				<h3><span id="hs_cos_wrapper_social_title" class="hs_cos_wrapper hs_cos_wrapper_widget hs_cos_wrapper_type_text" style="" data-hs-cos-general-type="widget" data-hs-cos-type="text">Share</span></h3>\r\n        \r\n        \r\n        	<div class="module">\r\n        		<span id="hs_cos_wrapper_Social_Sharing" class="hs_cos_wrapper hs_cos_wrapper_widget hs_cos_wrapper_type_social_sharing" style="" data-hs-cos-general-type="widget" data-hs-cos-type="social_sharing"><a href="http://www.facebook.com/share.php?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.psmbrokerage.com%2Funiversal-american-certification%3Futm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dfacebook" target="_blank" style="width:24px;border-width:0px;border:0px;"><img src="https://static.hubspot.com/final/img/common/icons/social/facebook-24x24.png" class="hs-image-widget hs-image-social-sharing-24" style="max-height:24px;max-width:24px;border-width:0px;border:0px;" width="24" hspace="0" alt="Share on Facebook"></a>&nbsp;<a href="http://www.linkedin.com/shareArticle?mini=true&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.psmbrokerage.com%2Funiversal-american-certification%3Futm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dlinkedin" target="_blank" style="width:24px;border-width:0px;border:0px;"><img src="https://static.hubspot.com/final/img/common/icons/social/linkedin-24x24.png" class="hs-image-widget hs-image-social-sharing-24" style="max-height:24px;max-width:24px;border-width:0px;border:0px;" width="24" hspace="0" alt="Share on LinkedIn"></a>&nbsp;<a href="https://twitter.com/intent/tweet?original_referer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.psmbrokerage.com%2Funiversal-american-certification%3Futm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dtwitter&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.psmbrokerage.com%2Funiversal-american-certification%3Futm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dtwitter&amp;source=tweetbutton&amp;text=Universal%20American%20Certification" target="_blank" style="width:24px;border-width:0px;border:0px;"><img src="https://static.hubspot.com/final/img/common/icons/social/twitter-24x24.png" class="hs-image-widget hs-image-social-sharing-24" style="max-height:24px;max-width:24px;border-width:0px;border:0px;" width="24" hspace="0" alt="Share on Twitter"></a>&nbsp;<a href="https://plus.google.com/share?url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.psmbrokerage.com%2Funiversal-american-certification%3Futm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dgoogle_plus" target="_blank" style="width:24px;border-width:0px;border:0px;"><img src="https://static.hubspot.com/final/img/common/icons/social/googleplus-24x24.png" class="hs-image-widget hs-image-social-sharing-24" style="max-height:24px;max-width:24px;border-width:0px;border:0px;" width="24" hspace="0" alt="Share on Google+"></a>&nbsp;<a href="mailto:?subject=Check%20out%20https%3A%2F%2Fwww.psmbrokerage.com%2Funiversal-american-certification%3Futm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Demail%20&amp;body=Check%20out%20https%3A%2F%2Fwww.psmbrokerage.com%2Funiversal-american-certification%3Futm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Demail" target="_blank" style="width:24px;border-width:0px;border:0px;"><img src="https://static.hubspot.com/final/img/common/icons/social/email-24x24.png" class="hs-image-widget hs-image-social-sharing-24" style="max-height:24px;max-width:24px;border-width:0px;border:0px;" width="24" hspace="0" alt="Share on Email"></a></span>\r\n        	</div>\r\n        \r\n      </div>\r\n    </div>\r\n  </div>\r\n  <div id="content">\r\n  	<div id="main" class="left_main">\r\n    	<span id="hs_cos_wrapper_main" class="hs_cos_wrapper hs_cos_wrapper_widget hs_cos_wrapper_type_rich_text" style="" data-hs-cos-general-type="widget" data-hs-cos-type="rich_text"><p><span style="color: #ff9900; font-size: 24px;"><strong>UAM 2019 Traning and Certification is Now Open</strong></span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 15px;"><span style="color: #262626;">We are pleased to announce that our 2019 Universal American (UAM) Training &amp; Certification portal is now open at <span style="text-decoration: underline;"><span style="color: #0000ff;"><a href="http://www.sentinelelite.com/." style="color: #0000ff; text-decoration: underline;" target="_blank">http://www.sentinelelite.com/. </a></span></span></span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 15px;"><span style="color: #262626;">As in previous years, you must first take your Medicare CORE and FWA training through an online educator like Gorman Health Group. This training is available now through Gorman and the following services: </span></span></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><span style="font-size: 15px; color: #444444;">America’s Health Insurance Plans (AHIP)</span></li>\r\n<li><span style="color: #444444; font-size: 15px;">Pinpoint Global Communications</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 15px;"><span style="color: #262626;">If you complete your CORE and FWA through Gorman Health group, your certificate will automatically populate in the system when you begin your UAM-specific Corporate, Products, and Procedures (CPP) Training at <span style="text-decoration: underline;"><span style="color: #0000ff;"><a href="http://www.sentinelelite.com/" target="_blank" style="color: #0000ff; text-decoration: underline;">http://www.sentinelelite.com/</a></span></span> and you will be ready to begin UAM training and certification. If you use AHIP or Pinpoint to obtain your CORE/FWA training, you will be directed to upload your certificates into the UAM training site on Sentinel Elite. </span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 15px;"><span style="color: #262626;">While there is no charge for UAM’s training and certification program, you are responsible for any expenses related to CORE certification completed through Gorman or the other online training services. When you take the UAM training modules, you will have up to three attempts to pass with a grade of 85% or higher. Please note that additional attempts will not be granted. </span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 15px;"><span style="color: #262626;">For complete information about UAM’s Training &amp; Certification program, please click here to review our Training and Certification FAQ. When Using Sentinel Elite: </span></span></p>\r\n<ul>\r\n<li><span style="font-size: 15px;"><span style="color: #262626;">Be sure to disable pop-ups on your computer, so that the Certification can run smoothly.&nbsp;</span></span></li>\r\n<li><span style="color: #444444; font-size: 15px;">Call the Sentinel Elite Call Center at (888) 568-0270 for questions regarding logging-in and accessing Certification.</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 15px;"><span style="color: #262626;">Be ready when Medicare Marketing begins on October 1, 2018. Begin your 2019 Medicare Core and FWA Training today! </span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 15px;"><span style="color: #262626;">Agent Support Have questions about this year’s training and certification requirements? Contact UAM Sales Support at 1-855-225-1475, Monday-Friday, 8:30 a.m. to 5:00 p.m. Eastern Time. </span></span></p>\r\n<p><span style="font-size: 15px;"><span style="color: #262626;">Y0067_AGT_TrainCertOpensRev2_0816 IA 08/29/2018</span></span></p></span>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div id="right">\r\n    </div>\r\n  </div>\r\n  <div id="footer_container">\r\n      <div id="footer">Copyright © 2019 Precision Senior Marketing</div>\r\n  </div>\r\n</div>'),
