ring-24" style="max-height:24px;max-width:24px;border-width:0px;border:0px;" width="24" hspace="0" alt="Share on LinkedIn"></a>&nbsp;<a href="https://twitter.com/intent/tweet?original_referer=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.psmbrokerage.com%2Fwellcare-certification-instructions%3Futm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dtwitter&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.psmbrokerage.com%2Fwellcare-certification-instructions%3Futm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dtwitter&amp;source=tweetbutton&amp;text=2019%20WellCare%20Certification%20Instructions" target="_blank" style="width:24px;border-width:0px;border:0px;"><img src="https://static.hubspot.com/final/img/common/icons/social/twitter-24x24.png" class="hs-image-widget hs-image-social-sharing-24" style="max-height:24px;max-width:24px;border-width:0px;border:0px;" width="24" hspace="0" alt="Share on Twitter"></a>&nbsp;<a href="https://plus.google.com/share?url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.psmbrokerage.com%2Fwellcare-certification-instructions%3Futm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Dgoogle_plus" target="_blank" style="width:24px;border-width:0px;border:0px;"><img src="https://static.hubspot.com/final/img/common/icons/social/googleplus-24x24.png" class="hs-image-widget hs-image-social-sharing-24" style="max-height:24px;max-width:24px;border-width:0px;border:0px;" width="24" hspace="0" alt="Share on Google+"></a>&nbsp;<a href="mailto:?subject=Check%20out%20https%3A%2F%2Fwww.psmbrokerage.com%2Fwellcare-certification-instructions%3Futm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Demail%20&amp;body=Check%20out%20https%3A%2F%2Fwww.psmbrokerage.com%2Fwellcare-certification-instructions%3Futm_medium%3Dsocial%26utm_source%3Demail" target="_blank" style="width:24px;border-width:0px;border:0px;"><img src="https://static.hubspot.com/final/img/common/icons/social/email-24x24.png" class="hs-image-widget hs-image-social-sharing-24" style="max-height:24px;max-width:24px;border-width:0px;border:0px;" width="24" hspace="0" alt="Share on Email"></a></span>\n        	</div>\n        \n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n  <div id="content">\n  	<div id="main" class="left_main">\n    	<span id="hs_cos_wrapper_main" class="hs_cos_wrapper hs_cos_wrapper_widget hs_cos_wrapper_type_rich_text" style="" data-hs-cos-general-type="widget" data-hs-cos-type="rich_text"><p><span style="color: #0362be; font-size: 24px;"><strong>2019 WellCare Certification is now available!</strong></span></p>\n<p><span style="font-size: 16px; color: #444444;"><strong>WellCare’s 2019 Annual Certification Training (ACT)</strong> has launched!</span></p>\n<p><span style="font-size: 16px; color: #444444;"><span style="color: #ff0201;"><strong>PLEASE READ:</strong></span>&nbsp;<span style="text-decoration: underline;"><span style="color: #3574e3;"><a href="/hubfs/WellCare-2019-AEP-Annual-Certification-Training-FAQ.pdf" rel=" noopener" target="_blank" style="color: #3574e3; text-decoration: underline;">WellCare 2019 Annual Certification Training FAQ</a></span></span></span></p>\n<p><span style="font-size: 16px; color: #444444;"><strong>2019 ACT Requirements:</strong></span></p>\n<ul>\n<li><span style="font-size: 16px; color: #444444;">Agents will have up to three attempts to pass the mastery exam with a minimum score of 85%.</span></li>\n<li><span style="font-size: 16px; color: #444444;">After each failed attempt, there is a lock out period of 24 hours before the exam can be attempted again.&nbsp;</span></li>\n<li><span style="font-size: 16px; color: #444444;">Failure to pass the third attempt will result in a suspended status for 6-months.</span></li>\n</ul>\n<p><span style="font-size: 16px; color: #444444;"><strong>2019 AHIP Completion and Submittal Requirements:</strong></span></p>\n<ul>\n<li><span style="font-size: 16px; color: #444444;">AHIP has released their 2019 Medicare Advantage and fraud, waste and abuse training on June 18<sup>th</sup>.&nbsp;</span></li>\n<li><span style="font-size: 16px; color: #444444;">New agents are required to complete the <strong>2019 AHIP,</strong> as part of their training requirement, prior to becoming certified with WellCare.&nbsp; (WellCare can no longer accept 2018 AHIP for new agents.) &nbsp;Completion of the 2019 AHIP will enable the agent to market/sell both 2018 and 2019 WellCare products.</span></li>\n<li><span style="font-size: 16px; color: #444444;">Transmitting completed AHIP to WellCare is easy.&nbsp; Simply have the currently certified agents access their AHIP homepage and click&nbsp;<em>Transmit&nbsp;</em>next to WellCare (1099). <span style="color: #3574e3;"><a href="https://urldefense.proofpoint.com/v2/url?u=http-3A__t3433669.icpro.co_track.aspx-3Fid-3D460-257C3464C5-257C5117-257C78-257C258-257C0-257C751-257C1-257C4C2083F5-26destination-3Dhttp-253a-252f-252fwww.ahipmedicaretraining.com-252fclients-252fwellcare-252f1099-26dchk-3DEF7CCBC&amp;d=DwMFAg&amp;c=9kXwhKegtYeqgWqETKbfKA&amp;r=piGSTfZN5S4ZQGfbjJZ3X-GFO97IFQtUcn3FNBxbF6Y&amp;m=Wt3l1ZcjlguN8oJMoUhWYATa3D1cRslKS2P5RPvqi9M&amp;s=21B-knVLe3h-THdIHqCK-CWU1fs6gjBNKjNMudTgwMo&amp;e=" style="color: #3574e3;">http://www.ahipmedicaretraining.com/clients/wellcare/1099</a></span></span></li>\n<li><span style="font-size: 16px; color: #444444;">New agents will need to use the WellCare/AHIP co-branded link above to transmit their completed AHIP to WellCare University. Via the link, they need to login to their AHIP account and complete the steps above.&nbsp;</span></li>\n</ul>\n<p><span style="font-size: 16px; color: #444444;"><em>Note: WellCare will not reimburse money paid towards training. </em></span></p>\n<p><span style="font-size: 16px; color: #444444;"><strong><em>**Currently certified agents must transmit 2019 AHIP and complete the 2019 ACT for TeleAgents no later than 9/30/2018 in order to remain certified on 10/1/2018.</em></strong><strong><em>&nbsp; Anybody not meeting this requirement will be moved to a suspended pending training status until all training requirements are met.</em></strong></span></p>\n<p><span style="font-size: 16px; color: #444444;">After all certification requirements are successfully completed, you will receive an email indicating you are certified to market/sell 2019 WellCare products.</span></p></span>\n    </div>\n    <div id="right">\n    </div>\n  </div>\n  <div id="footer_container">\n      <div id="footer">Copyright © 2019 Precision Senior Marketing</div>\n  </div>\n</div>');

